title: AirServer 5.0.3
description:
"AirServer is an AirPlay receiver for Mac and PC. It allows you to receive AirPlay feeds, similar to an Apple TV, so you can stream content or Mirror your display from your iOS devices or Macs running Mountain Lion or Mavericks.

AirServer delivers crisp 1080p HD mirroring and is specially optimized for iPhone 5s and its 64-bit processor. The update for AirServer is free for existing users, and gives you more features to make the things you do every day even better."

I needed an updated version of AirServer, lo an behold the internet provided but the files were password protected. I hate password protected piracy. So here you go, in all it's unprotected beauty.

KeyGen + Activator included.
